    java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Cloneable
    已过时。 
    Static routes are an undesirable exception to routes computed by a Router implementation and will not be supported in the future.

    @Deprecated
 @ScheduledApiChange(when="5.0")
public class StaticRoute
extends TCSObject<StaticRoute>
implements java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Cloneable
    Describes a sequence of Points that can be used as an alternative to dynamically computed routes for a Vehicle.
    另请参阅:
    Router, 序列化表格
